# Feature Spec: UK COPO Task & Document Handling for Claude Code Integration

**Author:** Lisa Wu  
**Role:** Principal Product Manager  
**Audience:** Engineering, Applied AI, Compliance  
**Status:** Final  
**Scope:** UK COPO only

---

## 1. Background

This feature enables correct integration with **Claude Code** for processing  
**UK COPO (Communications Data Production Order)** requests.

During discussions with **UK COPO NTAC**, several UK‑specific rules were confirmed that differ materially from other request types (e.g., US COPO, MLAT).  
These rules **override legacy assumptions** and must be enforced to prevent incorrect automation behavior.

This document defines the **authoritative detection logic**, **task model**, and **automation boundaries** for UK COPO processing.

